article_title: Negotiations Between Ukraine, Bondholders Take Step Backward
article_text:
After signs of progress in recent weeks, negotiations over Ukraine’s debt restructuring appeared to take a step backward Wednesday.

The Ukrainian government’s latest proposal over how to restructure $19 billion of debt is unacceptable to bondholders, a...
